    <entry>
      <title>GDB初探——代码实例</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="GDB-基本命令与功能"><a href="#GDB-基本命令与功能" class="headerlink" title="GDB 基本命令与功能"></a>GDB 基本命令与功能</h1><p>作为一个初学者，看见GDB有如下的功能觉得比较抽象和难以领悟其功能具体作用，于是我通过一段BFS来初探GDB，于是就有这篇博客啦！</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/dg1.png"></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/dg2.png"></p><h1 id="代码实例"><a href="#代码实例" class="headerlink" title="代码实例"></a>代码实例</h1><p>博主在这里采用无参运行的方式（因为有参运行出现了一些错误 :( ）</p><p>题目如下：</p><p>洛谷1135</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/%E9%A2%98.jpg"></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">bfs</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; set, <span class="type">int</span> s, <span class="type">int</span> e)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">bool</span>&gt; <span class="title">vis</span><span class="params">(set.size(), <span class="literal">false</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    queue&lt;pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; q;</span><br><span class="line">    q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(&#123;s, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> curr = q.<span class="built_in">front</span>().first;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> count = q.<span class="built_in">front</span>().second;</span><br><span class="line">        q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        queue&lt;pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; temp = q;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!temp.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;(&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; temp.<span class="built_in">front</span>().first &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;, &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; temp.<span class="built_in">front</span>().second &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;) &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        temp.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (curr == e) <span class="keyword">return</span> count;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">-1</span>; i &lt;= <span class="number">1</span>; i += <span class="number">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> next = curr + set[curr] * i;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (next &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; next &lt; set.<span class="built_in">size</span>() &amp;&amp; !vis[next]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                vis[next] = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(&#123;next, count + <span class="number">1</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> N, A, B, res;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 将输入硬编码</span></span><br><span class="line">    N = <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    A = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    B = <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; set = &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">5</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    res = <span class="built_in">bfs</span>(set, A, B);</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; (res == <span class="number">0</span> ? <span class="number">0</span> : res);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="编译准备并加载GDB"><a href="#编译准备并加载GDB" class="headerlink" title="编译准备并加载GDB"></a>编译准备并加载GDB</h1><h3 id="首先我们得保证运行的文件是可执行文件！"><a href="#首先我们得保证运行的文件是可执行文件！" class="headerlink" title="首先我们得保证运行的文件是可执行文件！"></a>首先我们得保证运行的文件是可执行文件！</h3><p>通过下图命令，我们不仅能生成可执行文件也能做好编译准备 <em>（ -g )</em></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%8F%AF%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%B9%B6-g.png"></p><p>启动</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/GDBload.png"></p><p>一开始博主是打算在运行的时候传入参数，但是刚开始出现了如下错误，发现是不能直接键入值的应该前面加一个run，再就是觉得传参稍显麻烦就将代码修改了一下变成了无参运行</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/%E5%B8%A6%E5%8F%82%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(gdb --args <span class="built_in">test</span> 5 1 5 <span class="comment">#加载前设置</span></span><br><span class="line">(gdb) <span class="built_in">set</span> args 5 1 5 <span class="comment">#运行前设置</span></span><br><span class="line">(gdb) run 5 1 5 <span class="comment">#运行时设置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="设置断点"><a href="#设置断点" class="headerlink" title="设置断点"></a>设置断点</h1><p>有两种设置断点方式</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/break1.png"></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/break2.png"></p><p>同时，在设置断点后可以通过两种方式来查看变量，一种是在到了断点后print变量显示，一种是在设置断点时通过command命令</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/command.png"></p><p>其中&gt;continue 也可以换成其他命令，比如&gt;next 等，根据需要设置</p><p>并且若觉得断点不必要可以删除，但貌似删除后编号还是保留的</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/rmbreak.png"></p><p>这是博主设置的断点位置</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/cpptxt.png"></p><h1 id="运行程序"><a href="#运行程序" class="headerlink" title="运行程序"></a>运行程序</h1><p>输入run 即可开始运行</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/run.png"></p><p>此时根据断点展示参数,其中一种会自动展示（即在设置断点时通过command命令）另一种则在来到断点后输入print</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/2wayprint.png"></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/02/Gdb%E5%88%9D%E6%8E%A2%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90/2wayprint2.png"></p><p>通过代码知，想从1层到5层（电梯每层上下升层数为3 3 1 2 5）需要先从1层到4层，再从4层到2层，再到5层，需要按3次电梯，这个数值设置使得负数层和超过最大层的楼层没有push进队列q里，体现BFS的特点，但vis的作用没怎么凸显，其中vis是防止程序陷入死循环，读者可以思考一下传入的参数去验证这个程序是否能避免死循环。</p><p>当输出结果3时程序已经不再运行，再输入continue显示</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The program is not being run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时按ctrl+c退出即可</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>一段代码能运行的蜕变之旅</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="蜕变须知"><a href="#蜕变须知" class="headerlink" title="蜕变须知"></a>蜕变须知</h1><p>一个可执行文件的前世今生是历经波折的，它需要经历以下过程:</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.jpg"></p><p>博主将在虚拟机上完成这一过程，重点放在汇编和链接部分。</p><h1 id="本次过程的目录结构"><a href="#本次过程的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="本次过程的目录结构"></a>本次过程的目录结构</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>README.md</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── include</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│ └── test.h</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">├── lib</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│ ├── libtest.a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│   main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">└── src</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> ├── main.cpp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> └── test.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：静态库libtest.a,main.cpp的头文件放在test.cpp中</p><h1 id="旅程启动！"><a href="#旅程启动！" class="headerlink" title="旅程启动！"></a>旅程启动！</h1><ul><li><p><strong>创建目录结构和文件：</strong></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>编写代码</strong></p><p>可以打开文件夹点击文件直接code,也可以运用vim</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA.jpg"></p><p>vim:</p></li></ul><p> <img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/vim.jpg"></p><p>  博主运行的代码很简单：</p><p>  test.h</p>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> TEST_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> TEST_H</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">printHello</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span> </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  test.cpp</p>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;test.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">printHello</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello from libtest!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  main.cpp</p>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;test.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printHello</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p><strong>编译源文件并创建目标文件：</strong></p><p>在运行下列命令是出现如下错误</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistake1.jpg"></p><p>原因是头文件并不在当前的目录里，我们需要去寻找头文件,<strong>在这里我们采用-I的形式</strong></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/touwj.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistak2.jpg"></p><p>但是又出现了错误，这是怎么回事呢？原来是我们需要把目标文件放在一个路径里，而我们此时没有创建。所以创建一个obj文件存放目标文件</p><p>再次执行,就生成了main和test的目标文件</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/obj.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>创建静态库 <code>libtest.a</code>：</strong></p><p>注意我们创建静态库的时候会出现权限不够的错误，因此命令为</p><p><img src="/https://Sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/staticlib.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>编译主程序：</strong></p><p>接下来就可以编译主程序啦！但是还是有错误，原来我们需要将main文件放置在一个路径里</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistake3.jpg"></p><p>创建好一个bin文件夹，就能正确编译了</p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/all.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>运行主程序</strong></p><p><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C.jpg"></p><p>（爱来自libtest!!!)</p></li></ul><h1 id="命令整理"><a href="#命令整理" class="headerlink" title="命令整理"></a>命令整理</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p project/include project/lib project/src</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/README.md</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/include/test.h</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/src/main.cpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/src/test.cpp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在project/src 路径下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建obj文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ -c main.cpp -I../include -o ../obj/main.o</span><br><span class="line">g++ -c test.cpp -I../include -o ../obj/main.o</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建静态库</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo ar rcs lib/libtest.a obj/test.o</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#编译主程序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建bin文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ obj/main.o -Iinclude -Llib -ltest -o bin/main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#运行主程序</span></span><br><span class="line">project/bin/main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Bhuman 2023 环境部署</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="BHuman-2023-Windows环境部署"><a href="#BHuman-2023-Windows环境部署" class="headerlink" title="BHuman 2023 Windows环境部署"></a>BHuman 2023 Windows环境部署</h1><p>博主依据BHuamn的官方文档逐步配置环境,期间出现了较多问题和需要注意的事项，特此整理出这篇博客，希望能帮助到大家！<a href="https://github.com/bhuman/BHumanCodeRelease">点击此处跳转BHuamnCoderealse</a>以及<a href="https://docs.b-human.de/coderelease2023/getting-started/initial-setup/">BHuman setup</a>。</p><h2 id="代码下载"><a href="#代码下载" class="headerlink" title="代码下载"></a>代码下载</h2><p>可进入github直接clone或者下载压缩包，但官方代码还需要要额外配置。<br>博主这里有直接的代码压缩包和必要的库<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DDZfELteZrhSOPlQ8hrsTQ">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DDZfELteZrhSOPlQ8hrsTQ</a><br>  提取码：26aw  </p><p><strong>注意要将all文件夹放在util文件目录下！</strong>   </p><h2 id="软件准备"><a href="#软件准备" class="headerlink" title="软件准备"></a>软件准备</h2><ul><li>VS 2022<br>若初次安装可在安装时勾选使用c++的桌面开发、通用Windows平台开发即可，视情况还可安装其他以后需要的功能比如python开发等<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131154616.jpg"></li><li>CMake 3.21.2<br>注意版本与官方文档要求的一致</li></ul><h2 id="编译代码"><a href="#编译代码" class="headerlink" title="编译代码"></a>编译代码</h2><ul><li>双击位于目录下的generate.cmd，使其能正常运行并自动pop出（出现error则对应error去检查）<strong>此时会生成Build文件夹</strong></li></ul><p><code>Make/Windows/generate.cmd</code>  </p><ul><li><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164101.jpg"><br><em>例如博主一开始CMake版本不匹配并且VS不是2022版本出现了如下错误</em><br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131160615.jpg">  </li><li>在<code>Build/Windows/CMake</code>找到<code>B-Human.sln</code>右键选择以VS 2022方式运行<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131161637.jpg">  </li><li>设置为release方式，右键SimRobot，选择生成<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163107.jpg"><br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163209.jpg">  </li><li>博主在release遇到了如下错误<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163600.jpg"><br>通过调整项目属性部分解决了<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131162317.jpg"><br>但是还是出现常量中有换行符的问题，在CSDN搜索了一下解决方法，然后尝试在出现错误的地方（即有双引号的地方）在后引号前加了一个空格键，问题解决<br><img src="/project/project/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164101-1706932303720.jpg"><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/annjeff/article/details/90070344?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522170653508116800185871336%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&request_id=170653508116800185871336&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduend~default-1-90070344-null-null.142%5Ev99%5Epc_search_result_base7&utm_term=C2001&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">链接</a>  </li><li>运行Simbot<br>项目正常运行后会弹出SimRobot程序，如图<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164409.jpg"><br>或者在<code>Build\Windows\SimRobot\Release</code>点击程序运行<br><img src="https://sothebylin.github.io/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164526.jpg"><br>从<code>Install/Scenes</code>选择文件打开，如果能成功打开则部署成功！</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
